<p>Open Instagram Insights every Monday. Look at which posts got the most reach, saves, and profile visits in the past 7 days. Double down on what works. Drop what does not.</p>
<p>Track DMs as leads in a simple spreadsheet. Note the source (which post or Story drove the message), the inquiry type, and whether it converted. After 30 days, you will see patterns that tell you exactly which content types generate revenue.</p>
<h3>Connect Instagram to Your Broader Strategy</h3>
<p>Instagram does not exist in a vacuum. The businesses that get the best results connect Instagram to their <a href="/blog/optimize-google-business-profile/">Google Business Profile</a>, their blog, and their <a href="/blog/get-more-google-reviews-local-business/">review strategy</a>.</p>
<p>Post a customer review screenshot on Instagram. Link to the full review on your <a href="/glossary/google-reviews/">Google Reviews</a> page. Share your latest blog post as a carousel. Every channel feeds the others.</p>
